Text: RE Brain TeaserI am not to bad off I got through seven right and almost got but had too many greats Denise Original Message From mailto Sent Thursday November PM To Subject Brain Teaser Forwarded by Dana DavisHOUECT on PM Embedded Enron North America Corp image moved to file From Dana Davis picpcx PM To cc Subject Brain Teaser Hey We get these newsletters in our apartments every month and there is always a brain teaser on the back side of it This was the one for this month Lets see how well you will do For every question tell me who this person is not their names but their relationship to you eg cousin aunt greatgrandma etc Who is your fathers uncles brothers sister Who is your aunts mothers fathers wife Who is your mothers nephews daughters son Who is your brothers sons sisters mother Who is your sisterinlaws fatherinlaws grandson Who is your sisters fathers stepsons mother Who is your uncles fathers grandchild Make an honest attempt and then scroll down for the answers Great Aunt Great Grandma rd Cousin Sisterinlaw Nephew Stepmother st cousin or yourself

RE Request for DirectionsAll I know is take south to Galveston Take the first st exit you will see the sign for Moody Gardens Turn right at the light Take it all the way to the Seawall Blvd which is the acutal seawall Turn left on the Seawall It will down on your left hand side The Galveston Hilton Resort and Conference Center Seawall Blvd Denise Original Message From mailto Sent Tuesday October AM To Subject Request for Directions Morning Would you mind terribly taking a few minutes to jot down a brief set of directions to our retreat in Galveston please sweetie little kitty Thank you DD

Blue Jean ShirtsHere is the information on the blue jean shirts The exact price is as follows M XL XXL XXXL Please turn in your money to me as soon as possible The total for all the shirts we have ordered is I have already made arrangements to pay for half up front due to such a high dollar order Pass the word on to those not on email Evelyn Morris Evelyn Jackson Nina NazirudDin Pamela Watts Annette Richardson Georgia Gillum Danise Johnson Jackie Stewart Marylyn Green Ethel Ford Cheryl Sumbler and Cheryl Curry We need to try and have the money by Powertime on Wednesday If you need an accomodation please let me know If you know of anyone else wanting a shirt please get with me as soon as possible I thought maybe the following might want a shirt Rev Jacque Bobbie Poledore Katherine Dailey Valerie Piper It would be nice if all women had one Also thank Joe Stewart when you see him for making all the arrangements for us Thanks Denise

Shirts for conferenceMorning I have information on the shirts we talked about for the Seeds of Praise conference Joe Stewart checked into both options we wanted For the polo style shirt it will be to per shirt For the long sleeve blue jean shirt it will be per shirt This is based on that the Northwest Printing will provide the shirts Also this will be the embroidered logo and not the iron on one We need to decide quickly and get our money turned in quickly We only have about weeks to get this done As we talked about we would wear these on Sunday for the closing worship service and then back to Veterans on Sunday Please either email your preference or let me know at Power time tonight If you know of anyone who is not on line and you have a few minutes to contact them today please do so Evelyn Jackson Ethel Ford Nina Nazir UdDin Pam Watts Cheryl Sumbler Cheryl Curry Danise Johnson and Evelyn Morris We need to make a decision quickly and try to have the money by Sunday Also if you have not finished paying your registration it is due by Friday so please try and bring it tonight otherwise you will have to catch up with myself or Bonnie on Friday Thanks Denise

FW Womens MinistryHere is the response from Ruby to our request for our Christmas meeting Please mark your calendars accordingly Also please add Ruby and her family to your prayer list Be Blessed Denise Original Message From Miles Ruby mailto Sent Tuesday September PM To MooreDenise I Subject RE Womens Ministry Hi Denise I really appreciate your note and yes it will be great and a tremendous BLESSING to see my sisters in Jesus I will place that on my calendar I generally take some time off that time of the year so I will be looking forward to it What a wonderful celebration it will be Since I live so far no one really has to help me but if they want to it would be greatly appreciated but mostly I hope that lots of ladies come When you told me that yall eat anything thats fine with me just let me know a few days in advance how many people you think will be coming and Ill be readyI love to have people come together in my home it will be a blessing There are several reasons that Im not available lately the main one being of course Im working approximately hours a day it is a very trying time for me right now and I need all the prayers that I can get please continue to do that the other reason is Im physically tired Im years old and have been having lots of responsibility for most of my adult years I was been blessed to be able to come back to Houston years ago and was afforded an opportunity to buy a new home and was at that time within minutes of my job not anymore hence I live quite a ways from church by distance approximately mi by time depending on whose doing the drivingsmiles and which way you come approximately min So after years and years of having to drive so far at least days a week Im tired God bless you and the Womens Ministry for thinking of me and my family at such a special time in any Christians life and I look forward to the fellowship Keep me posted Love and Gods grace to you Ruby Original Message From MooreDenise I mailto Sent Tuesday September AM To Subject Womens Ministry Importance High Good Morning Ruby I hope God has found favor with you this morning I have a request of you I dont know if you remember in May when we talked about having a womens ministry meeting at your home Well we met briefly last night and we are requesting that you your mother and aunt allow us to come and share with you during the Christmas holiday We would like you to cohost the meeting in December We are looking for a Saturday due to Pastor Wallace having class on Sundays now We would like to know if you would be willing to cohost on December The reason I say cohost is we always partner up with someone And we want to afford you the same opportunity Our meetings generally consists of prayer praise and worship We sing do bible study and just fellowship with one another During Christmas we also do a gift exchange We buy one gift for no one in particular put numbers on them and them draw the numbers out of a hat We thought the celebration of our Saviors birth would be a good time to come and pray with and for your family Please let me know I hope to see you soon We really have been missing you Be Blessed Denise

Womens Ministry Meeting Claudette Would you two be willing to cohost the November womens meeting Check your calendars to see if is available about pm Please let me know We are trying to finish out our calendar year Prayer on it and over it Dont forget the meeting tonight at pm at the church prior to the MOP meeting Denise

FW Prayer MinistryDont forget the meeting tonight Denise Original Message From Montgomery Claudette To MooreDenise I Sent PM Subject RE Prayer Ministry I wont I look so forward to this but thank you just the same youre so thoughtful Thanks Denise I will probably be a little late Chanel has class Did you notify Dana Original Message From MooreDenise I mailto Sent Monday August PM To Subject Prayer Ministry Carolyn Claudette Dont forget the prayer ministry meeting tonight at pm Denise

ReminderDana Carolyn Sending this email to remind you of the revival at Shaw Tabernacle UMC on Friday at pm The directions are S or S to E E to Wayside Exit Wayside and turn left under Take Wayside to Birmingham and turn right on Birmingham Birmingham dead ends into the church Try and be there on time because the church fills up pretty quickly Also remember the Seeds of Praise workshop on Saturday from am to pm at Mt Corinth UMC in Humble Take towards Humble Take the Y in the road when going into Humble onto Old Humble Road The church is about to miles down on the right If you pass Super KMart on the left turn around you have gone to far Breakfast will be served promptly at am I have already paid for all members going from Veterans so we can settle up later Dont forget the picnic is on Sunday after service If you havent signed up to bring anything contact Danise Johnson to see what is still needed If you need any other info please contact me Home Work Cell Pager Be Blessed Denise

FW PrayerGood Morning I pray that all is well with you this morning I wanted to share a prophetic word with you on this morning that went forth after our Building Fund committee meeting last night As shared with me by our First Lady Edith Wallace Bro Andrew shared a word that we as a people are to follow our Moses that God has given us and that God is calling all things to order He stated that when the Pastor speaks and gives a word of instructions we are to listen and stop bickering amongst ourselves like the children of Israel and follow the man of God He Bro Andrew stated that God said that if we as a church would unite and pray for the Pastor and his wife for the next days at and everyone be on one accord God said that He would move mightily This will be shared in an announcement on Sunday to let the church know this would be in line of things and that the church needs to get to a point of obedience because one of the reason why the church has gone around the mountain is because things have been out of order God is an awesome God and we want to give Him thanks for what He doing Please forward this information to as many people with contact information before Sunday Because this is something that we as a people can begin doing today and share the Word with the congregation on Sunday Have a wonderful God Blessed Day Denise
